      <title>尼日利亚采取新举措提振奈拉兑美元汇率</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-08/nigeria-central-bank-offers-dollars-at-1-101-naira-to-fx-bureaux</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尼日利亚推出了新措施来帮助该国遭受重创的货币，这可能有助于延续近期的涨势。]]></description>
